quran[7{c,v,t}:
9,80,"ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, tum khuwa aisay logon ke liye maffi ki darkhwast karo ya nah karo, agar tum sattar martaba bhi inhen maaf kardainay ki darkhwast karo ge to Allah inhen hargiz maaf nah kere ga is liye ke unhon ne Allah aur is ke rasool ke sath kufar kya hai, aur Allah fasik logon ko raah nijaat nahi dekhata"
9,81,"jin logon ko peechay reh jaane ki ijazat day di gayi thi woh Allah ke rasool ka sath nah dainay aur ghar baithy rehne par khush hue aur inhen gawara nah howa ke Allah ki raah mein jaan o maal se jehaad karen unhon ne logon se kaha ke"" is sakht garmi mein nah niklo"" un se kaho ke jahannum ki aag is se ziyada garam hai, kash inhen is ka shaoor hota"
9,82,"ab chahiye ke yeh log hansna kam karen aur royain ziyada, is liye ke jo badi yeh kamate rahay hain is ki jaza aisi hi hai ( ke inhen is par rona chahiye )"
9,83,"agar Allah un ke darmain tumhe wapas le jaye aur aindah un mein se koi giroh jehaad ke liye niklny ki tum se ijazat mangay to saaf keh dena ke,"" ab tum mere sath hargiz nahi chal satke aur nah meri mayt mein kisi dushman se lar satke ho, tum ne pehlay baith rehnay ko pasand kya tha to ab ghar bethnay walon hi ke sath baithy raho """
9,84,aur aindah un mein se jo koi marey is ki namaz e janaza bhi tum hargiz nah parhna aur nah kabhi is ki qabar par kharray hona kyunkay unhon ne Allah aur is ke Rasool Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam ke sath kufar kya hai aur woh marey hain is haal mein ke woh fasik thay
9,85,un ki maldari aur un ki kasrat aulaad tum ko dhokay mein nah daaley Allah ne to iradah kar liya hai ke iss maal o aulaad ke zareya se un ko isi duniya mein saza day aur un ki jaanen is haal mein nikleen ke woh kafir hon
9,86,jab kabhi koi surah is mazmoon ki nazil hui ke Allah ko manu aur is ke rasool ke sath jehaad karo to tum ne dekha ke jo log un mein se sahib mqdrt thay wohi tum se darkhwast karne lagey ke inhen jehaad ki shirkat se maaf rakha jaye aur unhon ne kaha ke hamein chore degiye ke hum bethnay walon ke sath rahen
